                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-182-off1064 t18090920-182-crimeloc1067"></join>. I was not at home when the beef was taken; about one or two o'clock I was sent for. The officer pursued the prisoner with the beef, and took it upon him. I knew the beef, it belonged to me, I cut it for a customer, and left it on the shop board to be sent home.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18090920-182-person1707">
